Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.45,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:51.82,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.20,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
