Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm so jealous.}Ghen tị ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'd like a little of that \Nconfidence for myself...}Mình cũng muốn tự tin như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.21,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I know!}Biết rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.72,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let's find a vocalist and write a song!}Tìm một ca sĩ và viết một bài hát!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.15,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Ryo can write the music,}Ryo có thể viết nhạc,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:19.50,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{and if you've got off-limits words, \NBocchi-chan, you should write the lyrics!}và em thì hãy suy nghĩ nên có thể viết lời được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.33,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Me?!}Em á?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.04,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Well? Great idea, huh?}Ý hay phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:27.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The nine years of lunch breaks \NI spent in school libraries...}Mình đã ăn trưa ở thư viện suốt 9 năm trời...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.30,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Was it all in preparation for this moment?}Chỉ để chuẩn bị cho ngày này sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.86,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{So, what will you do, Nijika?}Vậy cậu làm gì, Nijika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:33.86,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Go!}Ném!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Next, talk about quotas!}Tiếp theo là về chỉ tiêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.60,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Just shamelessly dodged that one, eh?}Đừng có né tránh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.09,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Um... What are quotas?}Chỉ tiêu là gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.15,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{The concert we did yesterday \Nis called a "booked concert."}Buổi diễn hôm qua gọi là "buổi diễn được đặt".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.44,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It's where the club assigns \Nthe band a ticket quota}Club sẽ giao cho ban nhạc chỉ tiêu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.65,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{to make sure enough people come.}để đảm bảo số người đến nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.85,Default,Club-kun,0,0,0,,{Your quota is ten tickets!}Chỉ tiêu là 10 vé!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:03.62,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Anything sold over the quota gets \Nsplit between the club and the band...}Phần vé bán dư ra sẽ được chia đôi với Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But if they can't bring in \Nenough to meet the quota,}Nhưng nếu không đủ chỉ tiêu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.76,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{the band has to pay the rest out of pocket.}thì ban nhạc phải trả bù cho phần thiếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.18,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{So until you get popular, it's a money pit.}Cho nên đến khi nổi tiếng thì nghèo mạt kiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.72,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's very concise!}Thẳng thắn ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.49,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{A bunch of my friends came \Nto yesterday's concert,}Hôm qua bạn bè chị đến nghe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.58,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{so we managed to meet our quota, but...}nên vừa đạt chỉ tiêu nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.91,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{After that performance, \Nthey likely won't be back.}Sau buổi diễn đó họ sẽ không đến nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.73,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You said it!}Phải đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.11,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And Ryo's got no friends, \Nso she'll be no help...}Ryo thì không có bạn nên chịu rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.85,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, do you—}Bocchi, em--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry! Forget what I said.}Xin lỗi, không có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.12,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Just please lose the dead fish stare!}Đừng làm ánh mắt cá chết nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've got plenty of imaginary friends, but...}Nếu là bạn tưởng tượng thì nhiều lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.48,Default,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,{You rock, Hitori-chan!}Cố lên Hitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.37,Default,Mai-kun,0,0,0,,{Living national treasure!}Bảo vật quốc gia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:48.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Anyway, since we'll need tens of thousands \Nof yen before our next concert,}Tóm lại là chúng ta sẽ cần vài chục\N ngàn yên trước buổi diễn tiếp theo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:52.12,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{let's get jobs to cover \Nthe quota and equipment!}hãy tìm việc làm để mua thiết bị và chạy chỉ tiêu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.38,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.88,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Jobs?!}Công việc?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.76,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That's the loudest I've ever heard you.}Lần đầu tiên em la to đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.70,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{No.}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.28,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I don't want to work. Too scary!}Em không muốn làm việc, đáng sợ lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.77,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Society is too scary!}Xã hội thật đáng sợ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.23,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{A piggy bank?}Heo đất?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.90,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{M-My mom was saving up for my wedding...}M-Mẹ em đã tiết kiệm để em làm đám cưới sau này...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.40,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But you can have it.}Nhưng chị có thể lấy nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.10,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Just... Please, no job...}Chỉ là đừng bắt em làm việc...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.67,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Don't make us the bad guys here!}Sao bọn chị cứ như trấn lột vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.39,DefaultTop,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Thanks, we'll take good care of—}Cảm ơn, bọn chị sẽ dùng nó thật tốt--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.96,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We're }{\i1}{not}{\i0}{ taking it!}Không có lấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.54,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We can't take money that \Nmeans that much to you!}Chúng ta không thể lấy tiền quan trọng đó được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:25.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna work!}Em không muốn làm việc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Because...}Bởi vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.55,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Welcome... Sh-Should I warm... up?}C-Chào mừng... T-Tôi làm nóng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.55,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It'd totally be like that...}Nhất định sẽ như thế luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.93,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H8F938D&\fs12\3c&HFBFEFB&\bord3.5\pos(132,55)}{Not this cashier who can't even make eye contact lmaoooooooooooooo}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Welcome... Sh-Should I warm... up?}C-Chào mừng... T-Tôi làm nóng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.93,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And then that...}Và sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:43.77,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs16\3c&H000401&\bord2\i1\4c&HDA76F3&\shad2\pos(134,296.5)}{Breaking\N}{\i0\fs20\shad0}{Defendant Hitori Gotoh's First Trial}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.19,DefaultTop,Prosecutor,0,0,0,,{For the crime of creeping out the customers,}Có tội vì làm khách hàng sợ hãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.77,DefaultTop,Prosecutor,0,0,0,,{we seek the death penalty!}Yêu cầu tử hình!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.28,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,{Okay, here comes the ruling...}Vậy thì xin phép công bố bản án...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.29,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,{Death!}Tử hình!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And then that!}Nhất định là thế rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.53,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{...cchi-chan.}Bocchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.77,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan.}Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.96,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.04,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You weren't listening, were you?}Nãy giờ không nghe gì hết phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.30,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry!}X-Xin lỗi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.07,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What were you saying?}C-Chị nói gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.03,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,Em sẽ làm ở đây với bọn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.11,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Here?}Ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.08,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You won't have to be scared \Nif you're with me and Ryo!}Không cần lo, có chị với Ryo mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:12.75,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs18\c&H110B07&\pos(332.5,287.5)}{Talk about Quotas}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.75,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It's a homey and harmonious place to work.}Là một nơi ấm cúng và thoải mái để làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.76,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We can serve drinks, and clean, \Nand see all kinds of bands!}Chúng ta phục vụ nước, dọn dẹp và quan sát các ban nhạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.76,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Don't wanna work... Don't wanna work...}Không muốn... không muốn làm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.76,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Well? What do you think?}Em nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Say no, girl!}Mau từ chối đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Say no!}Từ chối!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{You have to say no!}Phải nói không!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.27,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll dwu mwy bwest...}Em... sẽ cố...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.81,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Really? Thanks so much!}Thật hả? Cảm ơn nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sorry, girl...}Xin lỗi nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.17,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,{The job'll be more fun if we're all together!}Cả 3 làm với nhau sẽ vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It wouldn't be social anxiety \Nif we had the courage to say no.}Nếu đủ can đảm từ chối thì còn gì là sợ xã hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.63,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'll manage the band's funds, then.}Chị sẽ quản lý quỹ nhóm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.40,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Um... Wouldn't it be better \Nto have Ryo-san do that?}Em tưởng chị Ryo chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.58,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{What's that supposed to mean?!}Vậy là sao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Listen, Bocchi-chan.}Nghe nè Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.14,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Believe it or not, \NRyo's a very irresponNhìn sible spender.}Nhìn vậy chứ Ryo không biết giữ tiền đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Her family's rich and she \Ngets a huge allowance,}Gia đình giàu có, tiền tiêu vặt không thiếu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.71,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{but she blows it all on instruments, \Nso she's constantly broke!}nhưng lại đi mua hết vào nhạc cụ nên khi nào cũng nghèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.65,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Blush.}Xấu hổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.68,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{What part of that did you \Ntake as a compliment?}Có ai khen cậu hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.24,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Anyway, let's work hard \Nso we can play live again soon!}Vậy hãy cố hết sức đến buổi diễn tiếp theo nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.23,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Then we'll make our major \Ndebut in high school!}Sau đó là ra mắt ban nhạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We start work next week!}Tuần sau bắt đầu làm việc nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Come straight here after school!}Sau khi tan học thì đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.44,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Bocchi. Bye-bye.}Bocchi, tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.80,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:21.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And that first day of work is tomorrow.}Ngày mai là ngày đầu tiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've been in here for thirty minutes now.}Mình đã tắm trong bồn nước đá 30 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm bound to catch a cold, right?}Có lẽ là sẽ bị cảm lạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry... I'm sorry...}Xin lỗi, xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll work hard at everything except the job.}Em sẽ cố gắng tất cả trừ làm việc...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:36.09,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Mom! Sis is drowning!}Mẹ ơi! Chị đang chìm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Catch a cold! Catch a cold! \NCatch a cold! Catch a cold!}Mau bị cảm lạnh đi! Cảm lạnh đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:47.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Catch a cold!}Cảm lạnh đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.61,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Curse this good health of mine...}Sao cái cơ thể này khoẻ vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Then I'll just have to fake—}Giả bệnh thôi--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Nijika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.51,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Morning!}Xin chào!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.21,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0,0,0,,{First day of work, right?}Ngày đầu làm việc nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.35,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I know you're nervous, \Nbut we'll be there for you!}Biết là lo lắng nhưng bọn này sẽ hỗ trợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.41,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let's work hard together!}Hãy cùng nhau làm việc nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:17.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{No fair being so nice while \NI'm trying to blow off work...}Tại sao lại động viên mình đến vậy chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{You've made me realize the \Nfoolish error of my ways.}Em đã nhận ra sự ngu ngốc của bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{For making an honest woman out of me, \Nyou have my boundless gratitude.}Vô cùng biết ơn vì đã giúp em nhận ra điều này.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.08,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{What is she talking about?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm here.}Đến rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Do it, Bocchi!}Cố lên Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:44.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Do it, Bocchi!}Làm đi Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Do it, Bocchi!}Làm đi Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Do it, Bocchi!}Làm đi Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.74,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Tickets don't go on sale until five o'clock.}5 giờ mới bán vé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.91,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{We're still getting ready here.}Vẫn đang chuẩn bị.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She works here?!}Nhân viên làm ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She thinks I'm up to no good...}Chị ấy nghĩ mình là kẻ đáng nghi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've got to clear this up!}Phải mau giải thích...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:02.17,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{C-C-C-C-C-Calm down...}B-B-B-Bình tĩnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.13,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{You're the one who needs to calm down.}Em mới là người nên bình tĩnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.53,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{So you're the new part-timer?}Em là người làm thêm mới à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.15,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{You should've just said so.}Vậy thì nói cho chị biết chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.60,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-S-S-S-Sorry!}X-X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.60,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{I'm the manager here. Nice to meet you.}Chị là quản lý ở đây, rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{V-Very nice to meet you...}M-Mong chị giúp đỡ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The manager's scary.}Đáng sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can't handle people like her.}Mình không đỡ nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Nijika-chan, come here quick!}Nijika-chan, mau đến đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:24.80,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're the guitarist \Nwho played in the box.}Cơ mà em là tay ghita trốn trong thùng cacton nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.07,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Wasn't it... Mango Kamen?}Mango Kamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A new nickname?}Biệt danh mới à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.88,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I like you, Manager!}Mình thích chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.54,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-I'm Mango Kamen!}E-Em là Mango Kamen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.92,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That is }{\i1}{not}{\i0}{ her name!}Tên em không phải thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:40.12,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Don't go giving her weird nicknames, Sis!}Đừng có đặt biệt danh vớ vẩn nữa chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sis?!}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.88,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{You're Nijika-chan's sister?}Là chị gái của Nijika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.52,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I told you before.}Nói trước rồi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.49,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{When you first came to Starry, remember?}Lần đầu đến Starry ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:51.08,Flashback,Nijika,0,0,0,,{The club we're gonna play at \Nis called Starry.}Hôm nay chúng ta sẽ chơi ở Club gọi là Starry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.10,Flashback,Nijika,0,0,0,,{My big sister's the manager there.}Chị của chị quản lý chỗ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.60,Flashback,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Actually, our family lives \Nin the apartments above it.}Cơ mà nhà chị sống ở căn hộ phía trên.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.61,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{My heart was pounding so loud \Nthat I didn't hear her.}Lúc đó lo lắng quá nên chả nghe gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.57,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-R-R-Really?}V-Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.21,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That means you don't have to be so nervous.}Chị đã nói em đừng lo lắng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.69,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Right, Sis?}Nhỉ chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.28,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Call me "Manager" here.}Gọi là quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.18,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{And keep our work and private \Nrelationships separate.}Và đừng có mang quan hệ cá nhân vào công việc.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.48,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Don't scare her like that!}Đừng doạ em ấy nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.87,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H847AB4&\3c&HB9B9C4&\bord1\fs16\fax0.8\frz26.67\pos(228.5,125)}{Good Kid\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hApple 100}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.87,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\c&H091612&\frz225\fs14\fax0.3\pos(485.5,325)\}{Okaka}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:19.29,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's clear the tables first.}Đầu tiên dọn bàn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.81,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{When that's done, we'll wipe them all down...}Xong xuôi thì xử lý luôn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.24,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Huh? Where's Bocchi-chan?}Ủa? Bocchi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.45,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I needed a breather \Nin a dark, cramped place.}Xin lỗi, em cần hít thở ở nơi tối tăm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.72,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You need a breather already?!}Nhanh quá vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:36.49,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Here, Bocchi-chan, come over \Nand learn the drinks.}Nè Bocchi, qua đây học về nước uống nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.68,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Tonic water comes out of here,}Nước tăng lực ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{and beer comes out of this dispenser.}Bia thì từ chỗ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.94,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{The cocktails are on the shelf behind...}Cocktail ở trên kệ phía sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-I'll never remember it all!}S-Sao nhớ được!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:46.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Too fast!}Nhanh quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I just... mummummmmm...}Mình....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:54.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll have to infuse the knowledge \Ninto me through song!}Phải truyền kiến thức vào thông qua bài hát!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.99,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Where did that come from?!}Lôi đâu ra vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:59.13,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Cocktails are in the rightmost shelf!}Cocktail ở kệ ngoài cùng bên phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You're scaring me!}Đừng làm chị sợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.01,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,Tequila!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.01,DefaultTop,PA,0,0,0,,{They seem fun.}Trông có vẻ vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you're learning the drinks,}Tuy vui vì em có thể nhớ được...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.50,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{but why don't you set the guitar down?}nhưng sao không đặt cây ghita xuống?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.40,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,Kahlua!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.50,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,Rum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.30,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Hey, are you listening?}Nè, em có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:09.22,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Weird... She seemed kind of \Ncrappy at the concert, but...}Lạ nhỉ? Con bé diễn lúc trước tệ lắm mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.22,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You're not, are you?!}Có nghe không hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.94,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{She's good.}Con bé giỏi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.88,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You're seriously scaring me!}Đừng làm chị sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:15.63,DefaultItalics,Seika,0,0,0,,{Nijika's trying so hard to stop her, \NI don't think she realizes it...}Nijika đang cố gắng cản con bé nên có khi không nhận ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.63,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,{P-Please! Come back to us!}M-Mau quay lại đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.12,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.22,DefaultItalics,Seika,0,0,0,,{But I recognize that sound from somewhere.}Nhưng âm thanh của con bé quen lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.22,DefaultTop,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.81,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Get to work!}Làm việc đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.96,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Why me?!}Tại sao đánh em?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.94,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{For drink service, just pour the \Ndrinks they order and hand them over.}Phục vụ nước thì chỉ cần đổ ra ly và mang đến thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.92,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.86,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{They can pay 500 yen \Non top of the ticket price}Có thể trả thêm 500 yên,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.95,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{to get a drink ticket.}để có vé uống nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{500 yen per drink?}500 yên 1 phần?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:38.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And why a drink ticket system?}Tại sao lại bán vé đồ uống?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:41.08,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Stop staring like it's totally alien to you.}Đừng có nhìn như chị là người ngoài hành tinh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:45.08,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Clubs like this are actually \Nconsidered restaurants.}Club cũng như nhà hàng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.35,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I don't know all the details,}Chị không hiểu rõ lắm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:51.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{but apparently it's super hard to get a \Nbusiness license to run just a concert venue.}nhưng nghe nói rất khó \Nxin giấy phép để tổ chức trình diễn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.64,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I... I see!}V-Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:58.76,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{So we offer drinks \Nand operate like a restaurant.}Thế nên mới nghĩ ra bán vé đồ uống như một nhà hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.22,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Are you listening?}Em có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Working at a restaurant is advanced stuff!}L-Làm việc ở nhà hàng là công việc có độ khó cao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can't believe I cleared that bar so soon!}Không thể tin mình có thể clear sớm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Is this... personal growth?!}Đây là... trưởng thành?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.90,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b0\c&H525A56&\3c&HEAF2EE&\bord1.8\4c&H5CC7D5&\shad2\pos(497,256.5)}{Loneliness Hill}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:14.82,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Hey, customers already!}Khách hàng đến rồi kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.28,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We're about to be busy, Bocchi-chan!}Chúng ta sẽ bận rộn lắm đó, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:19.33,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b0\c&H525A56&\3c&HEAF2EE&\4c&H5CC7D5&\bord1.8\shad2\pos(497,256.5)\t(28,3907,\c&H353836&\3c&H9B9B9B&\4c&H576A63&)}{Loneliness Hill}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:17.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wait... Customer service already?!}Khoan đã... chưa gì đã phục vụ khách hàng?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What do I say?!}Phải nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:26.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{"Thank you for your royal parentage..."}"Cảm ơn vì dòng dõi hoàng tộc..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's not it!}Nói nhảm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{J-Just give me a practice run, please!}P-Phải luyện tập gấp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-No, wait! Stop it!}Không, khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.63,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(149,1)\an8\c&H1F242A&\3c&HE8EEEB&\bord2.5}{Thanks for coming!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.84,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,97)\an8\fs12\c&H1F242A&\3c&HE8EEEB&\bord2.5\frz358.7\pos(393,232)}{Thanks for coming!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.80,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She closed up!}Đóng cửa luôn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.30,Default,Customer A,0,0,0,,{Excuse me! One cola, please!}Một cola ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.49,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Coming!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan, cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:40.82,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Coming up!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.65,Default,Customer B,0,0,0,,{I'll have a ginger ale.}Tôi một ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.31,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Coming up!}Có ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.28,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, show some \Nrespect for the customers!}Bocchi, như thế là thất lễ đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.45,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-B-But I'm not ready!}N-N-Nhưng em đã chuẩn bị tinh thần!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.98,DefaultItalics,Ryo,0,0,0,,{We're losing the club's inherent darkness.}Chúng ta đang đánh mất sự tối tăm của Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{One oolong and one highball!}Một highball và trà ô long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.16,Default,Customer C,0,0,0,,{Where's the bathroom?}Nhà vệ sinh đâu ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.79,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Down the hall to your right, \Ndoor on the left!}Dưới sảnh cửa bên phải ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I experienced no personal growth whatsoever.}Cuối cùng mình vẫn chẳng trưởng thành...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.29,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, look!}Bocchi-chan, nhìn kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.76,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,{Here they are!}Họ đến rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.74,Default,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Hey, there! We're Alexandism!}Xin chào! Alexandism đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.36,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Our second album goes on sale today,}Album thứ 2 của bọn tôi sẽ ra mắt hôm nay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{They're pretty good, y'know?}Bọn họ tuyệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.64,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{so we're back to doing concerts,}thế nên sẽ diễn một buổi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It's a good time to relax.}Thả lỏng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.40,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,hi vọng mọi người sẽ mua nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.76,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Once the performances start, \Nwe'll have time to kill.}Khi bắt đầu diễn thì chúng ta rảnh lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.31,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.40,Default,hitori,0,0,0,,{Right...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.31,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Good work.}Vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.25,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Good work!}Vất vả rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:26.88,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{We tried to make every single \Nsong better than our first album,}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Don't you have to sell tickets?}Cậu không bán vé à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.88,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Manager stepped in for me.}Quản lý thay ca rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.12,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{All of today's bands are really popular,}Mấy ban nhạc hôm nay toàn nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:31.02,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{and if you haven't bought it yet, \Nwe're about to play some of those songs,}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.02,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{so she told me to watch and learn.}Nên chị ấy kêu ra đó mà học hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.11,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That's my sister for you.}Chị tớ là kiểu đó đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.25,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{so if you like them, please buy the album!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She's a tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun...}Tsun tsun tsun tsun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:38.23,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{And there's something I want \Nto tell you guys first.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.23,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{...dere. You know?}...dere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.30,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Excessive tsun.}Nhiều tsun quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:41.44,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{The crowd rocked pretty \Nhard at our last concert!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.44,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-S-Sorry...}X-X-Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.43,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Not only did I fail to help you,}Không chỉ vô dụng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:45.71,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{So after it was over, a guy came up \Nand offered up his card.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.71,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I couldn't even make eye \Ncontact with the customers.}Mà em thậm chí còn không dám nhìn khách hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.07,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Want this?}Dùng nó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:50.59,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{And we were so nervous. "Is this time \Nfor our major debut?" we thought.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.23,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Sorry it's not for mangos.}Tuy không phải thùng mango.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.59,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{No, thank you.}Không cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.62,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{But it would look pretty lame to let it show,}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.67,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You're doing fine!}Không sao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:56.51,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{so after a beat we just said, \N"Hello, welcome."}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.51,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It's your first day. You'll get used to it!}Mới ngày đầu thôi mà. Sẽ quen ngay thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:01.23,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Habits can be scary, huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:03.85,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why are you so nice to a \Nsub-water-flea like me?}T-Tại sao lại tốt với đứa như em vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.85,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{The words that came out of my mouth}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:08.14,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{were the words I've said a million \Ntimes at my part time job.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.77,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You know...}Chị ấy nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.88,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{According to the guy who gave us his card,}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.88,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I really like this club.}Thực sự yêu quý Club này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:16.44,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{he wanted to listen to the band \Non after us today, Tidaman,}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:16.44,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But here and reception are the only places \Nclub staff interact with the customers,}Nhưng chỉ chỗ này và quầy lễ tân \Nlà nơi duy nhất tiếp xúc khách hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.83,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{but we don't get along with them, \Nand we really wanna outshine them,}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.83,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{so I want to do my best to make \Nother people like it, too.}Vì vậy chị muốn cố hết sức để mọi\N người có thể thích nơi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.80,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{so we hope you listen to Alexandism too!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.21,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm s-s-sorry.}E-Em xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I w-worked so badly at a place \Nthat means so much to you...}E-Em đã làm việc không tốt tại nơi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.75,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{No, no.}Không không.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:29.56,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Now, let me introduce the band!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That's not what I meant.}Ý chị không phải thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.75,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Always eating curry before a concert, with his \Nown way of doing things... on bass, Matsuda!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.75,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I meant I want }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ to like \Nthis club too, Bocchi-chan.}Ý chị là muốn em thích nơi này nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.62,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{And the normal guy who always \Nhas our backs... on drums, Rei!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.62,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I want us to have fun working,}Chị muốn em vui vẻ làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.45,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{and to have fun playing.}Và vui vẻ chơi nhạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:43.36,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{He's got so many effects pedals he barely has \Nroom on stage to stand... on guitar, Koichi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.68,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Together.}Cùng nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:49.17,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{And on guitar and vocals, without \Nmuch to recommend him... me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:49.17,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{'Course, I also hope you'll be able to speak \Nto customers with a smile some day, too...}Dù gì thì cũng hi vọng\N có ngày em có thể tươi cười với khách hàng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.30,DefaultTop,Crowd,0,0,0,,Tsuyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.19,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0,0,0,,{Let's do this!}Lên nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.11,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It's starting, Bocchi-chan!}Bắt đầu rồi kìa Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The whole place is united.}Tất cả hoà làm 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The customers and the performers \Nare all enjoying themselves.}Khách hàng và ban nhạc đang vui vẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Meanwhile, at my concert...}So với buổi diễn của mình thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:15.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The customers paid 2,000 yen \Nto see that, didn't they?}Khách hàng bỏ 2000 yên để đến xem mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,So với mình thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:23.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna give them the same listless \Nconcert next time too, aren't I?}Nếu không thay đổi thì buổi diễn tiếp theo vẫn sẽ ảm đạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I want to make the effort to change, \Neven if only gradually,}Mình muốn cố gắng thay đổi nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and enjoy it with the rest of them.}và tận hưởng cùng mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.40,Default,Customer D,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.74,Default,Customer D,0,0,0,,{Orange juice.}Một nước cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{C-Coming up...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:51.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Look the customer in the eye. Interact.}Nhìn vào mắt khách hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Smile!}Cười!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Look her in the eye!}Nhìn vào mắt họ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Interact!}Cười!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.97,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Here you are.}C-Của quý khách đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan! Your eyes! Your eyes!}Bocchi! Mắt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.70,Default,Customer D,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.44,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Wow, that was nerve-wracking!}Lo lắng quá đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.55,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But great job!}Nhưng em làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.46,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You kept your head above the counter \Nand talked to her!}Em đã ngẩng đầu nhìn và nói chuyện rồi đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.50,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I did my best!}Em đã cố hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.07,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:22.45,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Having you here will make my memories \Nof today's concert even more fun.}Nhờ em mà buổi diễn hôm nay sẽ vui hơn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.45,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And you've taken a step forward.}Và em đã tiến thêm bước nữa rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.31,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A step...}Một bước...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A step.}Một bước.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A step?!}Một bước?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It feels like I took a thousand, though!}Cảm giác như còn cả quãng đường dài!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.35,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H3D583C&\pos(320,198.5)}{Tickets go on sale at }{\c&H25726A&}{5 pm}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.99,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Good work today.}Hôm nay vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.21,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Take care getting home.}Về nhà cẩn thận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:50.93,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye.}Chào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.63,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you for having me.}M-Mọi người vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.62,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Not leaving, Ryo?}Em không về à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.37,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Staying a little while first.}Em ở lại thêm chút nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.44,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?!}V-Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.89,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{See you later!}Gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:03.44,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes, s-s-s-see you tomorrow!}V-Vâng! Mai gặp lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's over!}Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I made it through an entire day somehow!}Mình đã sống sót qua hôm nay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{This work thing isn't as hard \Nas I thought it would be!}Không ngờ làm thêm cũng dễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll do my best again tomorrow!}Ngày mai sẽ cố gắng hết mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.08,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Achoo!}Hắt xì!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.09,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Eh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.86,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Bocchi worked hard, huh?}Bocchi đã cố gắng hết sức nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.38,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:27.12,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And she managed to say "see you tomorrow!"}Và em ấy còn nói mai gặp lại đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.77,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.26,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'm glad we formed this band.}Thật may khi lập ban với em ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Oh, right!}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.52,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let's send a LOINE message to Bocchi-chan.}Gửi tin nhắn nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.50,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'll say, "Let's keep it up tomorrow!"}Ngày mai cùng cố gắng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.94,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(231,1)\an4\c&H6D6D6D&\b0\fs9\pos(248.5,194.5)\3c&HF6F9F6&\bord1.5}{Nijika\N\h\h\h\hYou have a message}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.96,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{She's got an awful fever.}Sốt cao quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.34,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Dear, prepare a cold compress, would you?}Anh ơi, ra mua hộ em miếng dán hạ sốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.88,Default,Naoki,0,0,0,,{Does she need a trip to the hospital?}Có cần đến bệnh viện không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i0}{N-Now}{\i1}{ I get the fever...}S-Sao giờ lại sốt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:53.25,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Now that we've got Bocchi-chan on board...}Giờ thì đã có Bocchi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.87,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{All that's left...}Còn lại là...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.43,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{is to find a new vocalist!}tìm một ca sĩ mới!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:00.56,Default,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,{Who's this one for?}Ai chọn đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:03.54,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Me, me! It's me, it's me!}Là tớ nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:19.89,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{The tune that plays when my loneliness \Nand the pedal are stepped on}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:25.44,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Tracks down my cheeks over and over again}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:29.10,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{The pounding of my loneliness}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:33.20,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Is joined by the rhythm of the snare drum}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:36.29,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{To create a solid pulse}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:38.82,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Someone, please remove \Nthe distortion on my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:41.79,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{And take a look inside me}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:45.80,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Nobody can get inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:49.30,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{But it's the kind of night \Nwhen I hope someone will}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:51.80,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Distortion it's Motion}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.23,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Once it starts, there's no stopping it}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:59.45,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Limits can be overwritten with experience}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:00.79,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:02.85,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Distortion is always like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.31,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{My heart takes off, outpacing my left brain}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:08.95,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Toward where you are}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.58,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{An escort to the next note}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.30,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Distortion on my day-to-day anguish}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.14,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{The chord I play when I'm alone at night}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:18.60,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Is it the same for you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:21.22,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{I spent all those days chasing my ideal image}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:25.36,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Play an F chord with distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:29.40,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{So loud that the needle swings off the scale}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{Twenty more minutes... \NTwenty more minutes...}Còn 20 phút nữa... {Twenty more minutes... \NTwenty more minutes...}Còn 20 phút nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:39.78,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Watch it!}
